{"tid":1314060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［防帶風向］除咗P牌 重可以加個顯示被block人數？","createTime":"2019-07-14T04:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T03:58:05.000Z","uid":166661,"like":67,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9c0c1bd0b9a2634be44e9f61698aa354f6d77e0d","tid":1314060,"uid":166661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:28:09.000Z","msg":"本身有諗過得到既負皮到一定數目就顯示係名隔離 但係始終有人玩過膠未必有心<br />\n<br />\n我既建議係 被Block人數到一定數目就顯示係名隔離/有個標誌 個數目幾多就大家討論下（500？ 1000？） <br />\n廢老口吻：好人好者點會比咁多人block<br />\n<br />\n至少可以增加對家帶風向既成本？<br />\n唔係求其up一兩句就帶到風向<br />\n佢地都要思考點樣圓滑咁帶風向（可能令大家捉鬼難咗）<br />\n唔係改個名又可以出黎帶風向<br />\n<br />\n大家討論下？"},{"pid":"31e44686a24a9293de6071e734b087b49db6d174","tid":1314060,"uid":97776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"好似reddit karma system咁？"},{"pid":"c62f3f0568dff5f4c03b0f3ba47a6038134e52d3","tid":1314060,"uid":3647,"like":2,"dislike":23,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"連登信用系統<br />\n<br />\n預比人負評"},{"pid":"fcb9c63cfb91b7f0cb0a9ba79bcd1a8e445834c6","tid":1314060,"uid":166661,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c62f3f0568dff5f4c03b0f3ba47a6038134e52d3","tid":1314060,"uid":3647,"like":2,"dislike":23,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"連登信用系統<br />\n<br />\n預比人負評"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T05:15:43.000Z","msg":"顯示被block人數 唔會令你出唔到po<br />\n印象中舊登都可以睇被block人數"},{"pid":"9ccf0adfcb94b7eb3a14885c0423d1bf92f2188f","tid":1314060,"uid":153929,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"c62f3f0568dff5f4c03b0f3ba47a6038134e52d3","tid":1314060,"uid":3647,"like":2,"dislike":23,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"連登信用系統<br />\n<br />\n預比人負評"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T05:26:58.000Z","msg":"呢種信用係一人一票，合乎民主。<br />\n而你所講嘅信用系統係由有權力嘅政府評分，咁都混為一談，係咪批判思考模式出咗問題？"},{"pid":"f0cca3dfa55b72cd0b9ee8145fc2bf967d2437f1","tid":1314060,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score